---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
import { icons } from "../../components/icons";
---

<Base
  active="pit-notes"
  title="P3 at ICRA 2024"
  description="Three rookie drivers, one unfamiliar track, 41.8s laps in the final without a single bumper touch. What worked, what nearly didn't."
>
  <article class="article-wrap">
    <a href="/pit-notes/" class="article-back">
      <Fragment set:html={icons.arrowLeft()} />
      All pit notes
    </a>
    <div class="hero-eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:12px;color:var(--accent)">
      Race report · May 12 · 2026
    </div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(40px,6vw,64px);margin-bottom:16px">P3 at ICRA 2024</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub" style="margin-bottom:24px">
      Three rookie drivers, one unfamiliar track, 41.8s laps in the final without a single bumper
      touch. What worked, what nearly didn't.
    </p>
    <div class="article-byline">
      <span>By the perception crew</span>
      <span>·</span>
      <span>6 min read</span>
    </div>
    <div class="article-photo-slot">Race photo — to be provided</div>
    <div class="article-body">
      <p>
        [Article body — content to be provided. This is a sample layout showing type, spacing, and
        inline elements.]
      </p>
      <p>
        We arrived in Yokohama with a car we'd only driven on our own track. The first practice
        session made the problem obvious: the Vegas layout rewards late braking into T3, and our
        lookahead was tuned for wide entries.
      </p>
      <h2>The final</h2>
      <p>
        Twenty laps, head-to-head. The car preferred the inside line at T3 all weekend, so we let
        it. No bumper contact across the whole final — the safety margin came from the MPC
        fallback, not from driving slow.
      </p>
      <div class="tele" style="margin-bottom:32px">
        <div class="hero-eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:16px">Final · session data</div>
        <div class="tele-row"><span class="k">Best lap</span><span class="v red">00:41.8</span></div>
        <div class="tele-row"><span class="k">Avg speed</span><span class="v">7.9 m/s</span></div>
        <div class="tele-row"><span class="k">Contacts</span><span class="v">0</span></div>
        <div class="tele-row"><span class="k">Result</span><span class="v">P3</span></div>
      </div>
      <p>
        What nearly didn't work: the LiDAR mount loosened during quali and we caught it in the pit
        with 4 minutes on the clock. New thread-locker is now on the pre-race checklist.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="checkered" style="padding:24px 0">🏁</div>
    <a class="btn ghost" href="/pit-notes/" style="text-decoration:none">All pit notes</a>
  </article>
</Base>
